snippet.title: MetaDOS: BATTLE ROYALE JUST IN TIME | OFFICIAL ANNOUNCEMENT TRAILER
snippet.description:
MetaDOS: The Next-Gen Metaverse Battle Royale game.
Inspired by Apex Legend and In-Time movie. MetaDOS develop the game focused on E-sport battle royale mode with a time system (time is currency) along with high-quality graphics.
